{"tid":1574637,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【灣區風情】文革廢老殘害年輕人 - 程凱","createTime":"2019-09-16T13:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T13:45:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77dc8448f955ab4bd6b7c3195334925132bacd0f","tid":1574637,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190916/20769226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20769226&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=4d0d48a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20769226&h=18a64690\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190916/20769226</a><br />\n<br />\n【灣區風情】文革廢老殘害年輕人 - 程凱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190916/large/1568566829_de9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190916%2Flarge%2F1568566829_de9c.jpg&h=2408cb1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在連文革廢老都走出來製造動亂，林鄭實在不惜一切要殺掉香港一整代年輕人。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾聽說過日本人的一句話，印象極為深刻，他說「善良的中國人在文革已死清光」，因為有良知又正義的人，定必在那瘋狂時代反抗而被鬥死，只有貪生怕死或者窮凶極惡的人，才會有命殘存。<br />\n<br />\n前日愛國撐警大叔大媽四處圍毆香港年輕人，有如文革重臨，一班變老了的紅衛兵繼續遺禍作惡，亂打亂鬥製造社會混亂，而香港警察又淪落至從政者殺人武器，合演一場濫暴又濫捕的大龍鳳，對付敢於反抗的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n文革遺毒，揮之不去，中共昔日靠年輕人鬥死老人，今日則靠老人鬥死香港年輕人。完全想像不到一個政權要多窮兇極惡，才會這樣殘害社會的未來棟樑，現在連文革廢老都走出來製造動亂，林鄭實在不惜一切要殺掉香港一整代年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n世事都有因果報應，當年發動得文革，就有今日的國民質素，林鄭如此虐待港人子女，善良有為的下一代都會出走移民，賠上香港未來。保護孩子，從來我都以為是人的天性，但看看中國近期陷入的豬肉荒，其實都緣於地方政府過去為發展，趕絕低稅收的養豬業，最後連培育下一代優質豬種的畜戶都趕盡殺絕。世上只有極權政府，為求個人利益而殘害下一代。香港這個福地，面對中共打壓，回歸22年後仍孕育出一代有良知又敢於反抗的年輕人，蜚聲國際；對比中國以金錢掛帥的愛國教育，卻教出一班只懂炫富、不懂是非的中國留學生，出醜世界。<br />\n<br />\n可是，面對如此瘋狂的政府，希望我們不會是最後一代香港人。<br />\n<br />\n程凱<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/chengkaibayarea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fchengkaibayarea&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=acd78b03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/chengkaibayarea</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【鳴鏡高懸】民生政策 改革正面 (張一鳴)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【笑到最後】可預見的最壞情況 (高明)"},{"pid":"3737e986319a7faf44a9b5e0c9d911a5b1161f1d","tid":1574637,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=da84ecdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=020f11b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"32adb0f6c621da4b74f86bb478f58a73be57f973","tid":1574637,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"366a53a8cf14a24d2ce9ae4290e891f36a1dfbb9","tid":1574637,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44dc5f148bd9ece3a3c7f8c49aff5fe04d25827e","tid":1574637,"uid":536